  notes:
    - "Wave 674 (uu3406): __bool__, __str__, __repr__ dict-presence checks for uuid.UUID."
    - "uuid.UUID defines __str__ (true): str(UUID(...)) returns the standard UUID string form (e.g. '12345678-1234-...')."
    - "uuid.UUID defines __repr__ (true): repr(UUID(...)) returns UUID('12345678-1234-...')."
    - "uuid.UUID does NOT define __bool__ in its own __dict__ (false)."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

